<div class="container">
  <div class="header"><h1>💕 性格兼容性测试</h1><div class="lang-switch"><a href="index.html" class="active">中文</a><a href="../en/compatibility-test/" class="">EN</a></div></div>
  <div class="nav-back"><a href="../index.html">← 返回首页</a></div>
  <div class="section">
    <p style="color:#94a3b8;font-size:.85rem;margin-bottom:12px">输入两人的名字，回答关于彼此的问题，分析性格兼容性指数和相处建议。适合情侣、朋友、同事等关系。</p>
    <div id="inputSection">
      <div class="form-row">
        <div class="form-group"><label>名字1</label><input type="text" id="name1" placeholder=例如：小明></div>
        <div class="form-group"><label>名字2</label><input type="text" id="name2" placeholder=例如：小红></div>
      </div>
      <div class="btn-group">
        <button class="btn btn-primary" onclick="startTest()">开始测试</button>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div id="questionSection" style="display:none">
    <div id="q0" style="display:block">
      <p style="color:#e2e8f0;font-size:1rem;margin-bottom:16px">问题1/8: 一起做计划时，你们通常：</p>
      <div class="radio-group">
        <label><input type="radio" name="q0" value="0" onchange="nextQ(0)"> 很容易就大多数事情达成一致</label>
        <label><input type="radio" name="q0" value="1" onchange="nextQ(0)"> 经常有不同偏好</label>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div id="q1" style="display:none">
      <p style="color:#e2e8f0;font-size:1rem;margin-bottom:16px">问题2/8: 遇到分歧时，你们怎么处理？</p>
      <div class="radio-group">
        <label><input type="radio" name="q1" value="0" onchange="nextQ(1)"> 冷静地讨论</label>
        <label><input type="radio" name="q1" value="1" onchange="nextQ(1)"> 需要先冷静一下</label>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div id="q2" style="display:none">
      <p style="color:#e2e8f0;font-size:1rem;margin-bottom:16px">问题3/8: 你们理想的周末是：</p>
      <div class="radio-group">
        <label><input type="radio" name="q2" value="0" onchange="nextQ(2)"> 外出活动</label>
        <label><input type="radio" name="q2" value="1" onchange="nextQ(2)"> 宅家放松</label>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div id="q3" style="display:none">
      <p style="color:#e2e8f0;font-size:1rem;margin-bottom:16px">问题4/8: 你们的价值观和目标有多相似？</p>
      <div class="radio-group">
        <label><input type="radio" name="q3" value="0" onchange="nextQ(3)"> 非常一致</label>
        <label><input type="radio" name="q3" value="1" onchange="nextQ(3)"> 差异较大但互补</label>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div id="q4" style="display:none">
      <p style="color:#e2e8f0;font-size:1rem;margin-bottom:16px">问题5/8: 你们如何表达感受？</p>
      <div class="radio-group">
        <label><input type="radio" name="q4" value="0" onchange="nextQ(4)"> 直接坦率</label>
        <label><input type="radio" name="q4" value="1" onchange="nextQ(4)"> 用行动而非言语</label>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div id="q5" style="display:none">
      <p style="color:#e2e8f0;font-size:1rem;margin-bottom:16px">问题6/8: 当一方有压力时，另一方：</p>
      <div class="radio-group">
        <label><input type="radio" name="q5" value="0" onchange="nextQ(5)"> 提供情感支持</label>
        <label><input type="radio" name="q5" value="1" onchange="nextQ(5)"> 提供实际帮助和解决方案</label>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div id="q6" style="display:none">
      <p style="color:#e2e8f0;font-size:1rem;margin-bottom:16px">问题7/8: 你们一起的幽默感：</p>
      <div class="radio-group">
        <label><input type="radio" name="q6" value="0" onchange="nextQ(6)"> 很相似——笑点一致</label>
        <label><input type="radio" name="q6" value="1" onchange="nextQ(6)"> 不同但互相欣赏</label>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div id="q7" style="display:none">
      <p style="color:#e2e8f0;font-size:1rem;margin-bottom:16px">问题8/8: 你们如何处理个人空间？</p>
      <div class="radio-group">
        <label><input type="radio" name="q7" value="0" onchange="nextQ(7)"> 大部分时间在一起很舒服</label>
        <label><input type="radio" name="q7" value="1" onchange="nextQ(7)"> 需要定期的独处时间</label>
      </div>
    </div>

    </div>
    <div id="resultArea" style="display:none">
      <div class="personality-result">
        <div style="font-size:2.5rem;font-weight:900;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#06b6d4,#8b5cf6,#ec4899);-webkit-background-clip:text;-webkit-text-fill-color:transparent" id="scoreNum"></div>
        <div style="color:#94a3b8;font-size:.85rem;margin-top:4px">兼容性指数</div>
        <div class="type-badge" id="levelBadge"></div>
        <p class="type-desc" id="levelDesc"></p>
      </div>
      <div class="btn-group" style="justify-content:center;margin-top:16px">
        <button class="btn btn-primary" onclick="restart()">重新测试</button>
        <button class="btn btn-success" onclick="shareResult()">分享</button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="ad-slot"><ins class="adsbygoogle" style="display:block" data-ad-client="ca-pub-5998441792679372" data-ad-slot="XXXXXXX" data-ad-format="horizontal" data-full-width-responsive="true"></ins></div>
  <div class="seo-content">
    <h2>性格兼容性测试指南</h2>
    <p>兼容性测试从多个维度分析两人的匹配程度。虽然没有任何测试能完全捕捉人际关系的复杂性，但它们可以提供有用的洞察和话题。</p>
  </div>
  <div class="section"><h2>常见问题</h2>
<div class="faq-item"><h3>这个测试的原理是什么？</h3><p>测试基于性格特质互补理论，通过分析两人在沟通方式、价值观、冲突处理、兴趣爱好等维度的匹配度，计算综合兼容性指数。结果仅供参考和娱乐。</p></div>
<div class="faq-item"><h3>测试结果准确吗？</h3><p>这是一个趣味性测试，结果基于简单的性格匹配算法。真正的兼容性取决于双方的沟通、理解和努力。测试结果可以作为了解彼此的起点，但不应作为关系的唯一判断标准。</p></div>
<div class="faq-item"><h3>适合测试什么关系？</h3><p>Suitable for any relationship: couples, friends, colleagues, family, etc. Different relationships have different compatibility standards, and the test provides advice based on the relationship type.</p></div>
<div class="faq-item"><h3>数据安全吗？</h3><p>完全安全。所有计算都在浏览器本地完成，不会上传任何数据。</p></div>

  </div>
  <div class="ad-slot"><ins class="adsbygoogle" style="display:block" data-ad-client="ca-pub-5998441792679372" data-ad-slot="XXXXXXX" data-ad-format="horizontal" data-full-width-responsive="true"></ins></div>
  <div class="footer"><p>性格兼容性测试 - 纯前端本地处理 | 趣味工具</p></div>
</div>
<div class="toast" id="toast"></div>
<script>
function toast(m){var t=document.getElementById("toast");t.textContent=m;t.classList.add("show");setTimeout(function(){t.classList.remove("show")},2000)}

var answers = {};
var p1Name = '', p2Name = '';
var levels = {"high":{name:"默契十足",desc:"你们之间有很高的兼容性！你们在很多方面都能自然地理解和支持对方。继续保持真诚的沟通，这份默契会越来越深。"},"medium":{name:"互补成长",desc:"你们有适度的差异，这其实是关系的调味剂。差异让你们能从对方身上学到新东西。关键是尊重差异，在重要价值观上找到共识。"},"low":{name:"求同存异",desc:"你们有不少差异，但这不意味着关系不好。很多优秀的搭档正是因为不同才互补。重点是在核心问题上找到共同点，在日常差异上保持包容。"},};

function startTest() {
  p1Name = document.getElementById('name1').value.trim() || '甲方';
  p2Name = document.getElementById('name2').value.trim() || '乙方';
  document.getElementById('inputSection').style.display = 'none';
  document.getElementById('q0').style.display = 'block';
  document.getElementById('questionSection').style.display = 'block';
}

function nextQ(qi) {
  var radios = document.getElementsByName('q' + qi);
  for (var i = 0; i < radios.length; i++) {
    if (radios[i].checked) {
      answers[qi] = parseInt(radios[i].value);
      break;
    }
  }
  if (qi < 7) {
    document.getElementById('q' + qi).style.display = 'none';
    document.getElementById('q' + (qi + 1)).style.display = 'block';
  } else {
    showResult();
  }
}

function showResult() {
  // Calculate score: 0 answers contribute to compatibility, 1 answers contribute to diversity
  var compatScore = 0;
  for (var i = 0; i < 8; i++) {
    if (answers[i] === 0) compatScore += 12;
    else compatScore += 5;
  }
  // Add some name-based deterministic variance
  var nameHash = 0;
  for (var c of (p1Name + p2Name)) nameHash = ((nameHash << 5) - nameHash + c.charCodeAt(0)) | 0;
  compatScore += Math.abs(nameHash) % 15;
  compatScore = Math.min(99, Math.max(45, compatScore));
  
  var level = compatScore >= 80 ? 'high' : compatScore >= 60 ? 'medium' : 'low';
  var info = levels[level];
  
  document.getElementById('scoreNum').textContent = compatScore + '%';
  document.getElementById('levelBadge').textContent = info.name;
  document.getElementById('levelDesc').textContent = p1Name + ' & ' + p2Name + ' — ' + info.desc;
  
  for (var i = 0; i < 8; i++) {
    var el = document.getElementById('q' + i);
    if (el) el.style.display = 'none';
  }
  document.getElementById('questionSection').style.display = 'none';
  document.getElementById('resultArea').style.display = 'block';
  window.scrollTo({top: 0, behavior: 'smooth'});
}

function restart() {
  answers = {};
  document.getElementById('resultArea').style.display = 'none';
  document.getElementById('inputSection').style.display = 'block';
  document.getElementById('name1').value = '';
  document.getElementById('name2').value = '';
  for (var i = 0; i < 8; i++) {
    var el = document.getElementById('q' + i);
    if (el) {
      el.style.display = 'none';
      var radios = el.querySelectorAll('input[type=radio]');
      radios.forEach(function(r) { r.checked = false; });
    }
  }
}

function shareResult() {
  var score = document.getElementById('scoreNum').textContent;
  var text = p1Name + ' & ' + p2Name + ': 兼容性 ' + score + ' - 测试地址 https://free-toolbase.com/compatibility-test/';
  navigator.clipboard.writeText(text).then(function() { toast("已复制！"); });
}

</script>
<div id="feedback-widget" style="position:fixed;bottom:20px;right:20px;z-index:1000">
<button id="feedback-toggle" onclick="toggleFeedback()" style="width:48px;height:48px;border-radius:50%;background:rgba(6,182,212,.2);border:2px solid rgba(6,182,212,.5);color:#22d3ee;font-size:1.2rem;cursor:pointer;box-shadow:0 4px 12px rgba(0,0,0,.3)">💬</button>
<div id="feedback-panel" style="display:none;position:absolute;bottom:56px;right:0;width:320px;background:#1e293b;border:1px solid rgba(6,182,212,.3);border-radius:12px;padding:16px;box-shadow:0 8px 24px rgba(0,0,0,.4)">
<div style="display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;margin-bottom:12px"><span style="color:#f1f5f9;font-size:.95rem;font-weight:600">📝 反馈建议</span><button onclick="toggleFeedback()" style="background:none;border:none;color:#64748b;font-size:1.2rem;cursor:pointer">✕</button></div>
<textarea id="feedback-text" placeholder="请描述您的建议..." style="width:100%;height:100px;background:#0f172a;border:1px solid rgba(148,163,184,.2);border-radius:6px;padding:10px;color:#e2e8f0;font-size:.85rem;resize:vertical;outline:none;font-family:inherit" maxlength="1000"></textarea>
<div style="display:flex;justify-content:flex-end;margin-top:8px"><button onclick="submitFeedback()" style="background:rgba(6,182,212,.2);color:#22d3ee;border:1px solid rgba(6,182,212,.3);border-radius:6px;padding:6px 16px;font-size:.85rem;cursor:pointer">提交</button></div>
</div></div>
<script>function toggleFeedback(){const p=document.getElementById('feedback-panel');p.style.display=p.style.display==='none'?'block':'none';}
function submitFeedback(){const text=document.getElementById('feedback-text').value.trim();if(!text)return;const title=encodeURIComponent('Feedback - '+window.location.pathname);const body=encodeURIComponent('**Page**: '+window.location.href+'\n\n'+text);window.open('https://github.com/webtools-cn/tools-site/issues/new?title='+title+'&body='+body,'_blank');}</script>
<link rel="stylesheet" href="https://free-toolbase.com/related-tools.css">
<div id="related-tools-section" class="related-tools-section"><div class="related-tools-loading">Loading related tools...</div></div>
<script src="https://free-toolbase.com/related-tools.js"></script>
</body></html>